(1) The Certifying Authority may, at any time, alter any registration of any registered seed importer or registered seed cleaner upon application by the registered seed importer or registered seed cleaner , as the case may be, or by the personal representative of a deceased registered seed importer or registered seed cleaner or, in the case of an incorporated body being the registered seed importer or registered seed cleaner , as the case may be, by the managing director or the liquidator of such registered seed importer or registered seed cleaner .
